Happy release day @windwalkersofficial 🎉
Go stream the new album and make sure to watch the new music video for “The Overlook”! 🎥
Trevor and I wanted to pay homage to Stanley Kubrick’s “The Shining”, without ripping off or copying any scenes. I think we captured the feel of the film while creating something entirely our own. Either way, it was a super fulfilling project.. I adore these guys, and the whole team.
